<h2 class="bold font-l">Real In Rio (Beginning)</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The beginning of the movie Rio features this type of musical number. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="k41t0s" data-video-descrip="Miss Piggy's Fantasy is this, complete with synchronized swimming." data-video-title="&quot;Happiness, Miss Piggy&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/k41t0s_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/k41t0s.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BusbyBerkeleyNumber" data-video-tropename="Busby Berkeley Number" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/TheGreatMuppetCaper" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/k41t0s.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">"Happiness, Mis...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="ie4v2e" data-video-descrip="The Jades dance in honor of the beginning of Era 3." data-video-title="&quot;Together Alone&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/ie4v2e_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ie4v2e.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BusbyBerkeleyNumber" data-video-tropename="Busby Berkeley Number" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/StevenUniverse" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ie4v2e.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">"Together Alone"</span></p>
</a>
